" --- General Settings / 通用设置 ---
set nocompatible             " Use Vim settings that are compatible with older versions of Vim. 使用与较旧版本的Vim兼容的Vim设置

" --- Syntax Highlighting / 语法高亮 ---
syntax on                   " Enable syntax highlighting. 开启语法高亮

" --- Display Settings / 显示设置 ---
set number                  " Show line numbers. 显示行号
set ruler                   " Show cursor position in the status line. 在状态栏显示光标位置
set encoding=utf-8          " Set file encoding to UTF-8. 设置文件编码为UTF-8
set showmode                " Show current mode in the command-line. 在命令行显示当前模式
set showcmd                 " Show partial commands in the command-line. 显示已输入的部分命令

" --- Searching Settings / 搜索设置 ---
set incsearch               " Highlight matches while typing search patterns. 在输入搜索模式时高亮匹配项
set hlsearch                " Keep matches highlighted after search. 保持搜索匹配项高亮

" --- Indentation Settings / 缩进设置 ---
set tabstop=4               " Set the width of a tab character to 4 spaces. 设置tab键宽度为4个空格
set autoindent              " Copy indent from the previous line. 根据上一行自动缩进
